methods.name: public Builder setHasNetworkRequirement(boolean requiresNetwork)
methods.comment: * Sets whether a provider requires network access. False by default.

methods.name: public Builder setHasSatelliteRequirement(boolean requiresSatellite)
methods.comment: * Sets whether a provider requires satellite access. False by default.

methods.name: public Builder setHasCellRequirement(boolean requiresCell)
methods.comment: * Sets whether a provider requires cell tower access. False by default.

methods.name: public Builder setHasMonetaryCost(boolean monetaryCost)
methods.comment: * Sets whether a provider has a monetary cost. False by default.

methods.name: public Builder setHasAltitudeSupport(boolean supportsAltitude)
methods.comment: * Sets whether a provider can provide altitude information. False by default.

methods.name: public Builder setHasSpeedSupport(boolean supportsSpeed)
methods.comment: * Sets whether a provider can provide speed information. False by default.

methods.name: public Builder setHasBearingSupport(boolean supportsBearing)
methods.comment: * Sets whether a provider can provide bearing information. False by default.

methods.name: public Builder setPowerUsage(@PowerUsage int powerUsage)
methods.comment: * Sets a very rough bucket of provider power usage. {@link #POWER_USAGE_HIGH} by default.

methods.name: public Builder setAccuracy(@Accuracy int accuracy)
methods.comment:
* Sets a very rough bucket of provider location accuracy. {@link #ACCURACY_COARSE} by
         * default.
